## 六、参考实现方案

以下是一份**可直接复用**的 CSS + JSX 代码：

### CSS 文件新增

```css
/* ========== Mesh Gradient 动态背景 ========== */
@keyframes mesh-orbit {
  0%   { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
  25%  { transform: translate(-5%, 3%) rotate(2deg) scale(1.02); }
  50%  { transform: translate(3%, -4%) rotate(-1deg) scale(0.98); }
  75%  { transform: translate(-2%, 2%) rotate(1.5deg) scale(1.01); }
  100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
}

@keyframes mesh-orbit-reverse {
  0%   { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
  25%  { transform: translate(4%, -2%) rotate(-2deg) scale(0.98); }
  50%  { transform: translate(-3%, 5%) rotate(1.5deg) scale(1.03); }
  75%  { transform: translate(2%, -3%) rotate(-1deg) scale(0.99); }
  100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
}

.mesh-bg-container {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.mesh-bg-orb-primary {
  position: absolute;
  width: 200%;
  height: 200%;
  top: -50%;
  left: -50%;
  filter: blur(60px);
  opacity: 0.7;
  animation: mesh-orbit 16s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 90% 30%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.30) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 30% 60%, rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.25) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.40) 0%, transparent 60%);
}

.mesh-bg-orb-secondary {
  position: absolute;
  width: 170%;
  height: 170%;
  top: -35%;
  left: -35%;
  filter: blur(80px);
  opacity: 0.5;
  animation: mesh-orbit-reverse 20s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 10%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 90%, rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.10) 0%, transparent 50%);
}

/* 深色模式下增强显示 */
[data-theme="dark"] .mesh-bg-orb-primary {
  opacity: 0.5;
}
[data-theme="dark"] .mesh-bg-orb-secondary {
  opacity: 0.3;
}

/* 减弱动画（辅助功能） */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .mesh-bg-orb-primary,
  .mesh-bg-orb-secondary {
    animation: none;
  }
}
```

### JSX 组件

```jsx
// MeshBackground.js
const MeshBackground = () => (
  <div className="mesh-bg-container">
    <div className="mesh-bg-orb-primary" />
    <div className="mesh-bg-orb-secondary" />
  </div>
);

export default MeshBackground;
```

### 在 Layout.js 中使用

```jsx
import MeshBackground from '../UI/MeshBackground';

function Layout({ children }) {
  return (
    <>
      <MeshBackground />   {/* ← 添加到最顶层 */}
      <Sidebar />
      <main>{children}</main>
    </>
  );
}
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 上面的颜色已针对我们的**深色主题**做了调整（用了 indigo/purple/pink 替代 MeiGen 的蓝/紫/橙），你可以根据喜好调整色值。

